Dialogs.Text: Philler: Hey hey people, today we are going to cover a small squabble between two of your favourite Vloggers.
Philler: So, according to LoneFox33, Feat43 is using bots to inflate his subscriber count.
Philler: Feat has been previously known for his disdain of cheaters in gaming circles.
Philler: Quite ironic considered what Foxy has discovered.
Philler: According to him, Feat's videos have an impossible amount of views for his channel's size.
Philler: New videos of his just suddenly spiked from 1000 to 50000 views in a manner of days. Weird, considering his 1400 subscriber count.
Philler: Also, some of the comments in his videos are extremely suspicious, like they weren't written by people.
Philler: It seems that this cheater exposer have some explanations to give to his audience.
Philler: But that's not everything that we have to talk today, oh no, we are going to dig deeper into this bot farming bussiness.
Philler: We have plenty of stuff to get into, so let's get to it!
